\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}:\operatorname*{Ran}(f)\longrightarrow\left]a,b\right[$
\end_inset

, entonces 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f\circ f^{-1}=Id_{\operatorname*{Ran}(f)}
\]

